name: Dark Trip - SideQuest Exclusive Demo
summary: Psychedelic escape room where a player eats pills to solve puzzles. Welcome to one of the most unique and bizarre VR experiences, where you take on the role of an investigator searching for a missing woman — and are forced to consume drugs during your mission. The boundaries between reality, virtuality, and hallucinations dissolve, immersing you in a Lovecraftian nightmare. This is a trial version.
